replies.body:
I love getting this kind of feedback! We want to hear from the community even more when making changes like this so thanks for voicing your concerns with me!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 

There's still a lot to be revealed about how the new rune system will work, but rest easy knowing that you'll still be able to have fun with coming up different builds for different champs. I can't go into too much detail (mostly because I don't even have it yet xD) but you'll find a lot of details about how the new system will work [**right over here**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/features/coming-preseason-runes-reforged)!
